name: NEGATIVES  PACE / NEGATIVE S PACE / NEGATIVE  SPACE
description: Either at this point you either love these are absolutely hate them. It's difficult to tell; I see some heads turned sideways over there on the right. We're almost through the boomerang letter group part. I promise, just hold on. Just like in painting, music, sculpture or any kind of art form that matter...there's always playing with the negative space as mentioned in a previous image. This one happens to take it to the next level; inception style. I really love the negative space so much of these that I did one about negative space, no really the words negative space. Kinda meta right? Ughhh this is what I love about the English language. Can you see it or am I just nuts. Probably a little bit of both to be candid. Whew...the commentary is shorter and shorter...what a relief.
